# .Net build action

It builds the .Net ptoject.

## Inputs

| Name                    | Default   | Required | Description          |
| :---                    | :----     | :------: | :----                |
| app-name                |           | yes      | Application name     |
| dotnet-version          | 9.0.300   | no       | .Net version used to build, test and package the application |

## Outputs

None
